      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RICOCHET RIPPLE (7) did a good job to finish second last time out over 390m at this track (22.24) in a Mix 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. VELOCITY YIN (1) stalked the pace from a low draw last start and fought on well to finish 2.75 lengths away in third (16.84) at Q Straight in a Grade 5 over 300m. Can feature again. HOCKING (3) hit the ground running off the inside draw and there until late when holding on for a minor finishing second (19.27) at Q Straight in a Mix 5 over 350m. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from seven starts. Expecting another good run. OAK'S BEST (2) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
